<% title "Apply" %>
<div class="applications">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Applications </h1>
    <p>These are the Code the Change applications for the fall 2014 semester. The Deadline for these applications is Wednesday 9/10 at 11:59 PM. Thank you for showing interest in becoming a member of Code the Change! Please contact us at <%= mail_to "berkeley@codethechange.org" %> if you have any other questions about becoming a member.</p>
